  (title_block (title "Muon3 power, USB-C PD and SiPM bias") (date "2026-07-11") (rev "P0") (comment 1 "ARCHITECTURE - electrical capture pending"))
  (lib_symbols)
  (text "USB-C receptacle + battery + solar input -> protection -> TPS25751 PD controller + BQ2579x charger/power-path" (at 25 35 0) (effects (font (size 2 2)) (justify left)) (uuid "11000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001"))
  (text "Supports 20 V / 5 A contracts + onboard battery/solar. 5 V fallback: electronics boot only, HV permitted after checks, TECs HARDWARE disabled" (at 25 46 0) (effects (font (size 1.6 1.6)) (justify left)) (uuid "11000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002"))
  (text "Post-path protected bus (up to ~20 V) -> four Peltier bridges + bucks for 3V3 / 1V2 (FPGA). nRF9151 + RP2040 telemetry subsystem on always-on rail where possible." (at 25 59 0) (effects (font (size 1.6 1.6)) (justify left)) (uuid "11000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000003"))
  (text "TPS61170DRVR + inductor -> filtered adjustable ~30 V SiPM bias. Hardware OVP + EN default-off required." (at 25 72 0) (effects (font (size 1.6 1.6)) (justify left)) (uuid "11000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000004"))
  (text "PD contract status, battery presence, and power-good signals feed HARDWARE interlocks for TEC safety. Two 8-ch precision DACs (DAC80508) for thresholds + trims." (at 25 85 0) (effects (font (size 1.6 1.6)) (justify left)) (uuid "11000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000005"))
